msgid "[_hc](https://forum.f-droid.org/u/hans) has tagged and released [fdroidserver]({{ site.baseurl }}/docs/Installing_the_Server_and_Repo_Tools/) v1.0.4. This release finally fixes the problems mentioned [two weeks ago]({{ site.baseurl }}/2018/05/04/this-week-in-fdroid-w18.html). So if users of your repository are complaining that they [can't update](https://forum.f-droid.org/t/unable-to-get-apps-and-update-f-droid), please update ASAP!"
