msgstr "([Полный пример кода](https://gitlab.com/CalyxOS/platform_external_calyx_lupin/-/blob/e78b4e/updater/src/main/java/org/calyxos/lupin/updater/UpdateManager.kt#L154-168))"

#. type: Plain text
