#: _posts/2024-04-29-board-appointments-2024.md
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"> “As a passionate free software advocate and F-Droid user, I am delighted to bring my experience with community organizing and moderation to the Board in order to help the F-Droid project and community continue to grow equitably and inclusively into the future.”\n"
"> \\- Juliana Sims\n"
